<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">Depreciation</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">Equal to or more than the number of days in the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">Asset group depreciation threshold</strong> field</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">(Net book value of the fixed asset group on the date of depreciation) × (Rate of depreciation that is defined for the depreciation profile)</td>
</tr>
<tr sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Depreciation</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Less than the number of days in the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">Asset group depreciation threshold</strong> field</td>
<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="39">(Net book value of the fixed asset) × (Depreciation threshold percentage that is defined in the parameters) × (Rate of depreciation that is defined for the depreciation profile)</td>
</tr>
