<td sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">(Cost of acquisition) × (Depreciation threshold percentage that is defined on the <strong sourcefile="articles/finance/localizations/apac-ind-calculate-post-depreciation.md" sourcestartlinenumber="41">General ledger parameters</strong> page) × (Rate of depreciation that is defined in the depreciation profile)</td>
